Following his father's career, Sun Tiancheng, a Gen-Z embroiderer, has been trying to break through the traditional framework and bring new life to Chaozhou embroidery. Huang Baoyi, a member of the Lion Dancing Team, has been one of the few female dancers to be the "lion head." Growing up in the Internet Age, these Gen-Zers have been dedicated to inheriting the traditional Chinese art forms in their way.